# Static Website Hosting 
Hosting a HTTPS website by using AWS

## Cloud Services Used
- S3
- Route53
- Certificate Manager
- CloudFront
 ## Cloud Services Features
- S3:
-- 5GB of Free Storage
-- 20000 Free GET Requests & 2000 Free PUT Requests
- CloudFront:
-- 50 GB of free outbound data transfer
-- 2,000,000 free HTTP or HTTPS requests

- Route 53:
-- Free DNS queries for A records
- AWS Certificate Manager:
-- Free SSL/TLS certificate to create, and to use with CloudFront

